cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY

This paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval, as well as machine learning and data mining techniques for understanding news articles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). It could also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with extracting relevant information from text. Additionally, it involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it discusses the potential benefits of making news understandable to computers.
